fields_of_interest: Competition, Consumers, Justice and Fundamental Rights, Foreign and Security Policy and Defence, Digital economy and society, Borders and Security, Communication
eu_initiatives: Data Protection Reform, ePrivacy reform, NIS and cybersecurity implementations and initiatives, Telecommunications reform, Data markets and thereto associated initiatives, information rights and policies broadly when they affect individual rights.
subsection: Non-governmental organisations, platforms and networks and similar
relevant_communication: Dataskydd.net published a mostly bi-weekly newsletter in Swedish with data protection and privacy news. Additionally we make guidebooks, and present new strategies for privacy-preserving strategies for websites.
goals__remit: Dataskydd.net is a Swedish non-profit organisation aimed at promoting data protection interests of individuals in both legal and technical settings.
